OL,3,CSands Centre repair works in 'final
OL,4,Cstages' as re-opening date looms
OL,6,FCumberland Council says work on the
OL,7,FSands Centre is nearing completion,
OL,8,Fafter its re-opening was delayed
OL,9,Fseveral times.
OL,11,FWork is now going on inside the venue,
OL,12,Fwith the "finishing touches" being
OL,13,Fmade to the auditorium, including new
OL,14,Fseating, theatre lighting renewal, and
OL,15,Fa full refurbishment of the backstage
OL,16,Ffacilities.
