OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1780218421
OL,3,CSands Centre repair works in 'final
OL,4,Cstages' as re-opening date looms
OL,6,FLeader of Cumberland Council, Cllr
OL,7,FMark Fryer, said: "The necessary
OL,8,Frepairs and upgrades have been made,
OL,9,Fplus we have taken the opportunity to
OL,10,Fmake improvements to the events space."
OL,12,FThe entertainment venue was closed in
OL,13,FSeptember 2023 following the discovery
OL,14,Fof reinforced autoclaved aerated
OL,15,Fconcrete, or RAAC, in its roof.
OL,17,FIn February 2025 a temporary roof
OL,18,Fcanopy erected as part of the roof
OL,19,Freplacement was damaged by Storm
OL,20,FEowyn, which caused the temporary
OL,21,Fclosure of the Sand's leisure centre.
OL,26,@|D@Arb
