PN,35603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1780218421
OL,3,CSands Centre repair works in 'final
OL,4,Cstages' as re-opening date looms
OL,6,FApart from this, the Sands Centre's
OL,7,Fsports and recreation facilities have
OL,8,Fremained open.
OL,10,F200 tonnes of Raac roof panels have
OL,11,Fnow been removed and the replacement
OL,12,Froof installed, and the current
OL,13,Ftemporary roof is set to be removed
OL,14,Fthis week.
OL,16,FSixteen miles of scaffolding
OL,17,Fsurrounding the building site are also
OL,18,Fset to be dismantled.
OL,20,FCubby Construction is carrying out the
OL,21,Fworks on behalf of the council.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/4
