OL,3,CSands Centre repair works in 'final
OL,4,Cstages' as re-opening date looms
OL,6,FIts managing director Kirk Taylor
OL,7,Fsaid: "We've made significant progress
OL,8,Fover the last few months and pleased
OL,9,Fto report that our contracted works
OL,10,Fare set to be completed as planned."
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
